The presence of a PDB path string `D:\_w\1\b\bin\amd64\python.pdb` further supports this, indicating it's likely a compiled Python application (e.g., using PyInstaller). The binary itself does not contain any inherently malicious code; it's a standard wrapper for executing Python code.
